<P>
No one understands comedy and television better than Carol Burnett. There's 
certainly no better person to keep NBC on the top. Making sure that her "Carol 
&amp; Company" series is a consistent winner and promoting the show each week 
should be a priority for the network. 
</P>
<P>
Jane Gilliam, Santa Monica 
</P>
