Photo, COLOR, Clayton Williams Jr ; Photo, COLOR, In a room full of heads: 
Williams aims to become Texas' next leader. DANNY TURNER; Photo, COLOR, Ann 
Richards ; Photo, COLOR, At Richards' birthday party: from left, Lily Tomlin, 
Richards and Liz Carpenter, former press secretary for Lady Bird Johnson. BOB 
DAEMMRICH 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
