<DOCID> 295581 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 21, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Opinion; Part M; Page 1; Column 1; Opinion Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
