FRENCH FARMERS PROTEST 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
DIJON, France 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
About 50 farmers angered by government agriculture policies bombarded a 
government building with vegetables, paint and liquid manure during a 
late-night raid, police said Friday. Seven people were arrested. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
