<HEADLINE>
<P>
HOMEOWNERS NEAR AIRPORT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
There's been so much discussion of late about changing the airport name back to 
Orange County Airport that I would like to offer another idea. I think the 
airport should be named after someone who typifies Orange County, someone who 
symbolizes the county's greed and devotion to the haves taking it all from the 
have-nots. 
</P>
<P>
With this in mind, I would like to suggest that the airport be named the Donald 
Bren Airport. 
</P>
<P>
DONNA LAMPSON, Irvine 
</P>
</TEXT>
