<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A second 16-year-old suspect in the Fresno shooting rampage that left one dead 
and nine wounded will be tried as an adult. 
</P>
<P>
Juvenile Court Referee Phillip Silva ordered Friday that Dwight Tamplin stand 
trial as an adult for first-degree murder and 17 other criminal charges in 
connection with the Labor Day weekend shooting spree. Silva said Tamplin was 
