<P>
FOOTBALL PLAYERS; SAINT LOUIS CARDINALS (FOOTBALL TEAM); SENTENCING; BURGLARIES 
-- LOUISIANA 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA102190-0196 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 295954 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 21, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
