<P>
MILLER'S CROSSING (MOTION PICTURE); MOTION PICTURE PRODUCERS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA102190-0211 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 295993 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 21, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
