<HEADLINE>
<P>
AUCTION: VAN NUYS CONDOS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
An auction offering 49 contemporary condominiums at Cabrito Park Villas in Van 
Nuys will be conducted at 1 p.m. next Sunday by Kennedy-Wilson Inc. Minimum 
bids for the sale start at $85,000. 
</P>
<P>
The Mediterranean-style units at 8020 Langdon Ave., Van Nuys, range in size 
from 970 to 1,472 square feet, have 2 to 3 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths, cathedral 
ceilings and wood-burning fireplaces; common areas include courtyards and pool. 
</P>
<P>
Financing has been arranged by the seller. For further information regarding 
terms of sale, call (800) 933-0305 or visit the on-site information office, 
open daily from 10 a.m. to 6 p.m. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
